<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms and Conditions</title>
    <%- include('../partials/nav') %>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .terms-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(11, 11, 11, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color:rgb(136, 17, 241);
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color:rgb(136, 17, 241);
        }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #e9ebef;">
    <div class="terms-container">
        <h1 >Terms and Conditions</h1>

        <h2>General Conditions</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The rentor must provide valid identification and proof of employment or income.</li>
            <li>Rent payments must be made on or before the due date each month.</li>
            <li>No illegal activities are allowed on the property.</li>
            <li>Subletting the property is strictly prohibited without prior written consent from the owner.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Property Maintenance</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The rentor is responsible for keeping the property clean and in good condition.</li>
            <li>Any damages caused by the rentor or their guests must be reported and repaired at the rentor's expense.</li>
            <li>Major repairs and maintenance should be reported to the owner immediately.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Use of Property</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The property is to be used solely for residential purposes.</li>
            <li>Rentors must respect neighbors and adhere to noise regulations.</li>
            <li>Pets are only allowed with the owner's permission and must be properly cared for.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Termination of Agreement</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The rental agreement can be terminated by either party with a minimum of 30 days' notice.</li>
            <li>In case of a breach of the terms, the owner has the right to terminate the agreement immediately.</li>
            <li>Upon termination, the rentor must vacate the property and return all keys and access devices.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Security Deposit</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>A security deposit must be paid before moving in and will be held for the duration of the tenancy.</li>
            <li>The deposit will be returned within 30 days of vacating the property, minus any deductions for damages or unpaid rent.</li>
            <li>Any disputes regarding the deposit should be raised within 14 days of receiving the refund.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Insurance</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The rentor is encouraged to obtain renter's insurance to cover personal belongings and liability.</li>
            <li>The owner is not responsible for any loss or damage to the rentor's personal property.</li>
        </ul>

        

        <h2>Access to Property</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>The owner has the right to access the property for inspections, repairs, and maintenance with reasonable notice.</li>
            <li>In case of emergencies, the owner may enter the property without prior notice.</li>
            <li>The rentor should not change locks or security codes without the owner's consent.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
<%- include('../partials/foot') %>
</html>